utils.access

Class EncryptedAPS

  • java.lang.Object
    • utils.access.EncryptedAPS

  • public class EncryptedAPS
extends java.lang.Object
    wrapper around the raw data of an access permission set. Handles encryption. Class should not be public. Is only public for debugging.
